  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">v1: 8 pages, 2 Figures, v2: Published version, Journal title different, minor typographical changes, presentation improved, references added and updated. 9 pages, 3 Figures, Fig. 2 split into Fig. 2 and Fig. 3 for clarity</subfield>
